  "prompt": "Which are the most romantic movies?",
  "response": "Romantic movies are a beloved genre, and many films have captured hearts over the years. Here are some of the most romantic movies often celebrated for their love stories:\n\n1. **Titanic (1997)**\n   - Directed by James Cameron, this epic romance tells the story of Jack and Rose, star-crossed lovers aboard the ill-fated ship.\n\n2. **The Notebook (2004)**\n   - Based on Nicholas Sparks' novel, this film follows the passionate love story of Noah and Allie, spanning decades.\n\n3. **Casablanca (1942)**\n   - This classic film starring Humphrey Bogart and Ingrid Bergman features a poignant love story set against the backdrop of World War II.\n\n4. **Pride and Prejudice (2005)**\n   - Directed by Joe Wright and based on Jane Austen's novel, this film captures the romance between Elizabeth Bennet and Mr. Darcy.\n\n5. **Gone with the Wind (1939)**\n   - A sweeping epic, this film tells the turbulent love story of Scarlett O'Hara and Rhett Butler amidst the American Civil War.\n\n6. **Love Actually (2003)**\n   - Directed by Richard Curtis, this film intertwines multiple love stories, showcasing various facets of romance and relationships.\n\n7. **When Harry Met Sally... (1989)**\n   - A romantic comedy that explores the question of whether men and women can ever just be friends, starring Meg Ryan and Billy Crystal.\n\n8. **Am\u00e9lie (2001)**\n   - This whimsical French film follows the titular character, Am\u00e9lie, as she embarks on a quest to spread joy and ultimately finds love.\n\n9. **The Fault in Our Stars (2014)**\n   - Based on John Green's novel, this poignant film tells the love story of Hazel and Gus, two teenagers dealing with cancer.\n\n10. **A Walk to Remember (2002)**\n    - Another adaptation of a Nicholas Sparks novel, this film follows the transformative love between Landon and Jamie.\n\nThese movies are renowned for their touching love stories and have resonated with audiences worldwide. Whether you're in the mood for a classic romance or a contemporary love story, this list has something for every romantic at heart.",
